Docker plug-in setup in eclipse

Go to Eclipse Market place

select "Docker Editor 10.0" - CLick install it.

<<< Do not try below plug-in, it will not install properly >>>
"Eclisep Docker Tooling 4.2.0.201903121920" 


Then go to 

"Help" -> "Install New Software" (New windows will pop up)

In the "Work with:" Text box [https://download.eclipse.org/linuxtools/update-2019-03-docker]  (type this command)
Below you can see list of check box items, Please select all and as usual Next ---> next and finish.

Rest start the eclipse.

Go to "Windows" --> "Show View" --> in text box type docker (you will see all Docker Related info) select "Docker Explorer"




